descriptionHtml:
[color=#00ffff][size=4]This is Uthgerd the Unbroken exactly the same except she is younger and with the mark on her face removed and with her hair changed to another default style, as you can see she use to be a beautiful woman and now we can see her for who she truly is.[/size][/color]

[b][color=#ffff00]Two mods I used that I recommend you using if you haven't installed them yet.[/color][/b]
"Better females Version 3 " by Bella
"No More Blocky Faces" by Xenius
